        "description": {
            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "I'm using RC3 of ZF2. I have the following code:\r\n\r\n{code}$config = array(\r\n    'proxy_host' => 'xxx.xx.xx.xxx',\r\n    'proxy_port' => 80,\r\n);\r\n\r\n$adapter = new Zend\\Http\\Client\\Adapter\\Proxy();\r\n$adapter->setOptions($config);\r\n\r\n$client = new Zend\\Http\\Client();\r\n$client->setAdapter($adapter);\r\n$client->setOptions(array('timeout' => 4));\r\n   \r\n$client->setUri('https:\/\/www.phpgangsta.de');\r\n\r\n$response = $client->send();\r\n$body = $response->getBody();{code}\r\n\r\n\r\nIf the Uri is a HTTPS url or the proxy does a 301 redirect with a HTTPS target location, we get the following errors:\r\n\r\n\r\nNotice: Undefined index: sslverifypeer in XXXX\\Zend\\Http\\Client\\Adapter\\Socket.php on line 187\r\n\r\nCall Stack:\r\n    0.0694     349208   1. {main}() xxxxx.php:0\r\n    3.4962    2661336   2. Zend\\Http\\Client->send(???) xxxxx.php:71\r\n    9.3429    2859528   3. Zend\\Http\\Client->doRequest(???, ???, ???, ???, ???) XXXX\\Zend\\Http\\Client.php:808\r\n    9.3429    2859528   4. Zend\\Http\\Client\\Adapter\\Proxy->connect(???, ???, ???) XXXX\\Zend\\Http\\Client.php:1267\r\n    9.3429    2859592   5. Zend\\Http\\Client\\Adapter\\Socket->connect(???, ???, ???) XXXX\\Zend\\Http\\Client\\Adapter\\Proxy.php:83\r\n\r\n\r\nFatal error: Call to undefined method Zend\\Http\\Response::extractCode() in XXXX\\Zend\\Http\\Client\\Adapter\\Proxy.php on line 211\r\n\r\nCall Stack:\r\n    0.0694     349208   1. {main}() xxxxx.php:0\r\n    3.4962    2661336   2. Zend\\Http\\Client->send(???) xxxx.php:71\r\n    9.3429    2859528   3. Zend\\Http\\Client->doRequest(???, ???, ???, ???, ???) XXXX\\Zend\\Http\\Client.php:808\r\n   61.0842    2860576   4. Zend\\Http\\Client\\Adapter\\Proxy->write(???, ???, ???, ???, ???) XXXX\\Zend\\Http\\Client.php:1280\r\n   69.3014    2860920   5. Zend\\Http\\Client\\Adapter\\Proxy->connectHandshake(???, ???, ???, ???) XXXX\\Zend\\Http\\Client\\Adapter\\Proxy.php:122\r\n"
        },
